bomberman.core.logic.powerUp
Enum PowerUpEnum

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<PowerUpEnum>
      bomberman.core.logic.powerUp.PowerUpEnum
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<PowerUpEnum>
public enum PowerUpEnum
extends java.lang.Enum<PowerUpEnum>

The Enum PowerUpEnum is the access point for reflection-based instantiating PowerUps. In fact the specific PowerUp is not instanced since the Block in which it's contained doesn't expose it. Each enum value has a float point value that indicates its percentage of chance to appear and the PowerUp's specific class type.

Author:
Federico Scozzafava
